snippet: If it's a given that NFL officials will be criticized now and then, such bad-mouthing becomes that much more significant when some of the league's most prominent voices — Cam Newton, Richard Sherman, Josh Norman — rise in unison to com...
lead_paragraph: If it's a given that NFL officials will be criticized now and then, such bad-mouthing becomes that much more significant when some of the league's most prominent voices — Cam Newton, Richard Sherman, Josh Norman — rise in unison to complain about the men in stripes.

headline.main: ICYMI in NFL Week 8: Cam, Sherman, Norman Critique Officials
headline.print_headline: ICYMI in NFL Week 8: Cam, Sherman, Norman Critique Officials
